---
title: Creamy Rosé Shrimp Tortellini with roasted red peppers
description: This one is just like your favourite restaurant's cheesy tortellini! The creamy rosé sauce coats every piece of pasta, while shrimp and gooey mozzarella cheese make for an unforgettable takeout fake-out.
